<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-09-09T18:00:54-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-09-09T18:00:54-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T18:00:54-04:00</updated><title>达斯·维达 (Darth Vader) 的配音者詹姆斯·厄尔·琼斯 (James Earl Jones) 去世，享年 93 岁</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;James Earl Jones 2015 年的照片&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Po20x2izq8qJqIHblv4f3wIlQnE=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73575068/492713228.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Jemal Countess / Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;XwIRPy&quot;>;James Earl Jones，幕后杰出演员达斯·维达 (Darth Vader) 的声音，已于 &lt;a href=&quot;https://deadline.com/2024/09/james-earl-jones-dead-1236082801/&quot;>;根据 &lt;em>;Deadline&lt;/em>; 去世，享年 93 岁&lt;/a>;.&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;9rcy0j&quot;>;琼斯于 1931 年出生于密西西比州的阿卡布特拉。在克服了语言障碍后，琼斯继续了辉煌的演艺生涯，创作了数十部作品几十年来的戏剧、电视节目和电影。他在百老汇起步，于 1958 年在科特剧院（现称为詹姆斯·厄尔·琼斯剧院）主演&lt;em>;坎波贝洛的日出&lt;/em>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;jkh9fx&quot;>;然而，他的作品1977 年在第一部&lt;em>;星球大战&lt;/em>;中的角色给观众留下了巨大的印记，尽管&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cbsnews.com/news/james-earl-jones-dies-age -93-actor-darth-vader/#:~:text=琼斯%20请求%20his%20name%20not%20appear%20in%20the%20credits%2C%20out%20of%20deference%20to%20Prowse.%20[琼斯% 20would%20not%20be%20credited%20as%20the%20voice%20of%20Vader%20until%20the%20release%20of%20%22Return%20of%20the%20Jedi。%22]&quot;>;他最初并未被记入&lt;/a >; 出于对穿着达斯·维达套装的大卫·普劳斯的礼貌而为反派配音。虽然琼斯以其独特的声音而闻名&lt;em>;S...&lt;/em>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/ 24240301/james-earl-jones-darth-vader-voice-died&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240301/james-earl-jones-darth-vader-voice-died" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240301/james-earl-jones-darth-vader-voice-died</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T17:35:45-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T17:35:45-04:00</updated><title>您可以在此处预订 AirPods 4 和更新版 AirPods Max</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple AirPods 4 从包装盒中取出的特写图片，背景为灰色。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TPE_2I1YQ6pC9KpJoihu-rwICaE=/0x1:1463x976/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574984/AirPods_4_Press_Image.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple 现在销售四款不同的 AirPods，全部支持 USB-C 充电。&lt;/em>; |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Qah8ya&quot;>;与新的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239802/iphone-16-pro-max-hands-on -apple-photos-features-price&quot;>;iPhone 16&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24236958/apple-watch-series-10-hands-on-bigger-brighter- and-thinner&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 10&lt;/a>;，苹果在其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24237601/apple-iphone 期间发布了 AirPods 的三个新版本-16-event-announcements-products&quot;>;周一“It&#39;s Glowtime”活动&lt;/a>;。其中包括新款入门级 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/23313529/apple-airpods-4-noise-cancellation-price-features&quot;>;AirPods 4&lt;/a >; 售价 129 美元，购买高端 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239947/apple-airpods-4-hands-on-preview-features-anc&quot;>;AirPods 4具有主动降噪功能&lt;/a>;（ANC），售价 179 美元，以及修订后的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236804/airpods-max-second-gen-price -specs-features-release-date&quot;>;AirPods Max&lt;/a>; 售价 549 美元。这三款产品将于 9 月 20 日上市，今天即可预订。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;mzeW3e&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component =&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;AirPods Pro 2 很快将兼作助听器&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2024/9/9/24236881/apple-airpods-pro-second-gen-hearing-aid-protection-features-update&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 的 iPhone 16 活动：8 个最重大的公告&quot;,&quot; url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239739/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-watch-series-10-airpods&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;在哪里预订 Apple Watch Series 10和黑色 Apple Watch Ultra 2&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series-10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;} ]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;Z05s5J&quot;>;根据 Apple 的说法，两款新的 AirPods 4 型号的音质比 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/22744686/apple-airpods-third-gen-review&quot;>;第三代&lt;/a>;。它们还具有新功能，例如切换到 USB-C。 ANC 版本还在缩小的充电盒中内置了扬声器，使 Apple 的“查找我的”追踪器更加有效，并且无线充电可与 Qi 和 Apple 兼容...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/24240101/apple-airpods-4-max-headphones-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24240101/apple-airpods-4-max-headphones-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24240101/apple-airpods-4-max-headphones-preorder-buy-price-release-date</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T17:02:26-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T17:02:26-04:00</updated><title>在哪里预订 Apple Watch Series 10 和黑色 Apple Watch Ultra 2</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;多个不同颜色的 Apple 智能手表。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HKmtwHXNrsfefIy_OvKyUcXT9dE=/299x0:3541x2161/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574917/Apple_Watch_Series_10_lineup_240909.0. .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple 更新了其产品阵容，添加了新的颜色和功能，包括睡眠呼吸暂停警报。&lt;/em>; |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;iHg5y0&quot;>;iPhone 16 在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24237601/apple 期间成为焦点-iphone-16-event-announcements-products&quot;>;苹果公司周一举行的“It&#39;s Glowtime”活动&lt;/a>;，但这并不是唯一首次亮相的新产品。 Apple 还推出了全新 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236801/apple-watch-series-10-price-specs-features-release-date&quot;>;Apple Watch 系列10&lt;/a>; 以及现有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239740/apple-watch-ultra-specs-price-features-release-date 的黑色版本&quot;>;Apple Watch Ultra 2&lt;/a>;。两款产品均从今天开始接受预订，并于 9 月 20 日推出，Series 10 起价为 399 美元，最新的 Ultra 2 起价为 799 美元。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>; &lt;aside id=&quot;CNtfva&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 的 iPhone 16 活动：8 个最重大的公告&quot; ,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239739/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-watch-series-10-airpods&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 发布带有噪音的 AirPods 4取消和更好的声音&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/23313529/apple-airpods-4-noise-cancellation-price-features&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;: “您可以在这里预订 AirPods 4 和更新的 AirPods Max”，“url”：“https://www.theverge.com/24240101/apple-airpods-4-max-headphones-preorder-buy-price-release- date&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;kMZYJC&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 10 是 Apple 最薄的可穿戴设备，配备全新广角 OLED 屏幕，迄今为止，苹果在智能手表中使用的最大显示屏。这款新型可穿戴设备在 Apple 的 S10 SiP（系统级封装）上运行，并具有许多新功能，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240045/apple-watch-sleep- apnea-detection-feature-series-9-10-ultra-2&quot;>;包括睡眠呼吸暂停警报&lt;/a>;，这是一种人们停止呼吸的情况...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series-10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series-10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series-10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T16:58:24-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T16:58:24-04:00</updated><title> iOS 18 将于下周发布，提供自定义主屏幕的新方法</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;手持 iPhone 15 Plus。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/WNgG5XEYRWmOIjLF9STcPvWDg_c=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574893/236791_Apple_iPhone_15_and_15_Plus_review _DSeifert_0006.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Dan Seifert / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;jUc5nn&quot;>;Apple 公布了 iOS 18 的发布日期，距离发布仅几天时间。该更新将于 9 月 16 日发布，将添加自定义 iPhone 主屏幕和锁定屏幕的新方法。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;UMjeYT&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/ 6/10/24172132/apple-ios-18-new-features-ai&quot;>;在 iOS 18&lt;/a>; 中，您可以自由&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24196806/ios-18 -android-chaos&quot;>;在主屏幕上重新排列应用程序和小部件&lt;/a>;并更改其外观。 Apple 还推出了重新设计的控制中心，以及&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/14/24178564/apple-password-managers-lastpass-sherlock&quot;>;新密码管理应用程序&lt;/a>;并支持&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/10/24175479/ios-18-satellite-imessage-wwdc-2024&quot;>;卫星消息传送&lt;/a >;。其他一些更新包括消息中的新文本效果、改进的照片应用程序以及在邮件应用程序中组织收件箱的新方法。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;imuT4Q&quot;>;但是，此更新不包括&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/31/24209910/apple-intelligence-ios-18-preview-siri&quot;>;iPhone 15 Pro 和 &lt;a 即将推出 Apple Intelligence 功能&lt;/a>; href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24237017/iphone-16-specs-features-price-release-date-apple&quot;>;整个 iPhone 16 系列&lt;/a>;。即将推出的工具将帮助您重写和总结文本...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240230/ios-18-release-date -iphone-16&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240230/ios-18-release-date-iphone-16" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240230/ios-18-release-date-iphone-16</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T16:54:21-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T16:54:21-04:00</updated><title> AMD 放弃旗舰游戏 GPU——首先追逐人工智能</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/zkqw6znZkR3CDoqYTx-4ppyHr_A=/13x0:2040x1351/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73574881/twarren_201116_4300_0014.0.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Tom Warren / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;EUeIkB&quot;>;AMD 正在大声说出安静的部分：它现在优先考虑人工智能领先于游戏玩家旗舰 GPU 的芯片。该公司刚刚制定了一项新的业务战略，将把 RDNA 游戏图形和 CNDA 数据中心的工作合并成一个通用的“UDNA”，首先瞄准人工智能。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;HhUvnD&quot;>;在对 &lt;em>;Tom&#39;s Hardware&lt;/em>; 的两次采访中（你肯定会&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tomshardware.com/pc-components/gpus /amd-deprioritizing-flagship-gaming-gpus-jack-hyunh-talks-new-strategy-for-gaming-market?utm_medium=social&amp;amp;utm_source=twitter.com&amp;amp;utm_campaign=socialflow&quot;>;想要&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tomshardware.com/pc-components/cpus/amd-announces-unified-udna-gpu-architecture-bringing-rdna-and-cdna-together-to-take-on-nvidias-cuda -ecosystem&quot;>;阅读两者&lt;/a>;），AMD 计算和图形主管 Jack Huynh 并不拐弯抹角。他解释说，对于游戏显卡，现在的目标是以较低的价格建立规模和市场份额，而不是“山中之王”旗舰 GPU，因为后者尚未说服足够多的买家将 Nvidia 抛在身后。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;YMdEaz&quot;>;这是第一次采访的关键段落：&lt;/p>; &lt;blockquote>; &lt;p id=&quot;IwgSvx&quot;>;汤姆的硬件：就价格而言，你有......&lt; /p>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240173/amd-udna-gpu-ai-gaming-rdna-cdna-jack-huynh &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240173/amd-udna-gpu-ai-gaming-rdna-cdna-jack-huynh" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240173/amd-udna-gpu-ai-gaming-rdna-cdna-jack-huynh</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T16:40:19-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T16:40:19-04:00</updated><title> Beats 的新款 iPhone 16 保护壳可与相机控制按钮配合使用</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Beats 的新款 iPhone 16 保护壳系列。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/migkKziSXxI8ihOyNgR43Izu6LU=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574850/beats1.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Beats 的新款 iPhone 16 保护壳内部采用超细纤维衬里，有四种颜色可供选择。&lt;/em>; |图片：Beats&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;0rKkF0&quot;>;Beats，Apple 的其他产品&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236804/airpods-max- Second-gen-price-specs-features-release-date&quot;>;耳机&lt;/a>;品牌刚刚发布了其首款专为&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/设计的智能手机保护壳系列9/9/24230103/iphone-16-pro-specs-features-price-release-date-apple&quot;>;Apple 16 系列&lt;/a>;，与新的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/24239802/iphone-16-pro-max-hands-on-apple-photos-features-price&quot;>;相机控制按钮&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c -float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;NwH9tD&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;iPhone 16 Pro 和16 Pro Max上手：别叫它快门按钮&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239802/iphone-16-pro-max-hands-on-apple-photos- features-price&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;KiCyz1&quot;>;售价 49 美元的硬壳聚碳酸酯保护壳具有“柔性侧壁”，有助于吸收跌落时的部分冲击力，并且超细纤维衬里可保护 iPhone 的表面。根据 Beats 的说法，每个外壳的外表面都经过“光滑的防刮涂层”处理，这一功能可能是为了解决苹果的问题 - 并且 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2024/9/9/24240167/apple-finewriting-cases-dead&quot;>;现已停产&lt;/a>; — &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/12/23863322/apple-watch -series-9-iphone-15-case-finewriting-fabric-leather&quot;>;微斜纹 FineWoven 手机壳&lt;/a>;，容易出现划痕。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;aqRWTh&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MCFU4LL/A/beats-iphone-16-pro-max-case-with-magsafe -sunset-purple&quot;>;今天可通过 Apple 网站订购&lt;/a>;，有午夜黑、山顶石、激流蓝和日落紫配色，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240190/beats-apple-iphone-16-pro-max-cases-camera-control&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240190/beats-apple-iphone-16-pro-max-cases-camera-control" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240190/beats-apple-iphone-16-pro-max-cases-camera-control</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T16:32:26-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T16:32:26-04:00</updated><title>在第一部预告片中，该系列电影的电影宇宙看起来就像地狱一样</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9U35AKkKeCEQUNCPwdTJW4WPso0=/0x0:1920x1280/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574833 /jessica_hynes_daniel_bru_hl_isaac_powell_aya_cash_himesh_patel_lolly_adefope.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;电影片场中的一群人盯着镜头。 | HBO&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ntz6DT&quot;>;HBO 的母公司华纳兄弟探索频道 (Warner Bros. Discovery) 对&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/8/13 /23300237/dceu-ezra-miller-the-flashbatgirl-black-adam-david-zaslav&quot;>;构建注定失败的电影宇宙&lt;/a>;，但网络似乎在取笑阿曼多·伊安努奇这一切的混乱，萨姆·门德斯和乔恩·布朗的新系列&lt;em>;The Franchise&lt;/em>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;6Tv0jo&quot;>;以虚构的超级英雄电影&lt;em>;Tecto：风暴之眼&lt;的世界为背景&lt;正在深入制作，《特许经营权》紧随其后，影片的工作人员试图在一个似乎注定会失败的项目中度过难关。对于制作人员丹尼尔（希梅什·帕特尔饰）和达格（洛莉·阿德福普饰）来说，面对喜怒无常的演员和火灾恐慌，事情已经够困难的了。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;eVPUjW&quot;>;但是，当工作室高管过来发表与导演愿景相冲突的笔记时，片场的氛围变得……&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240191/hbo-the-franchise-trailer-premiere-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240191/hbo-the-franchise-trailer-premiere-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240191/hbo-the-franchise-trailer-premiere-date</id><author><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T16:18:20-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T16:18:20-04:00</updated><title> Apple 推出速度更快的 MagSafe 充电器，可与新款 iPhone 16 手机搭配使用</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;MagSafe 充电器连接到 iPhone 16 背面&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NUcdBP2TrLYTB-hmE7nT2atuMkA=/12x0:1746x1156/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574793/MX6X3_AV5.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Kw6vDW&quot;>;Apple 发布了新的、更强大的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MX6Y3LL/A/magsafe-charger-2-m?fnode=764064079c45c648b46b5614168d31c227879164ece336b6f96affb2f8cd98138c262e3b63d66c4dff9c75 的版本b56bc47369f8bc6ecdee9a04af7c2fb8b96e180182b8f106fb41eca3c44ba98fb5e81fb64967decf7b36e8501618091f540c4bb53a&quot;>;MagSafe 充电器&lt;/a>;在其&lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24237601/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-products&quot;>;9 月 iPhone 16 活动今天&lt;/a>;。该 puck 将与所有 iPhone 和任何 Qi2 设备兼容，但只有新款 iPhone 16 型号被列为支持最快 25W 无线充电速率。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;tbeXsS&quot;>;这比三星和谷歌目前提供的手机 - Galaxy S24 系列的最大功率为 15W，而使用第二代时，谷歌的 Pixel 9 手机的功率范围为 15W-23W &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22894924 /google-pixel-stand-2nd-gen-review-price-specs&quot;>;Google Pixel Stand&lt;/a>;。 （Pixel 9 型号只能使用标准 Qi 充电器进行 12W 充电。）&lt;/p>; &lt;blockquote>; &lt;p id=&quot;zoA1DR&quot;>;更快地实现高达 25W 的无线充电 — iPhone 16 在大约 30 分钟内可充至 50% 的电量和 iPhone 16 Pro 与 30W USB-C 电源适配器配对时（已出售...&lt;/p>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9 /24240184/apple-iphone-16-pro-25-watt-magsafe-charging&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240184/apple-iphone-16-pro-25-watt-magsafe-charging" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240184/apple-iphone-16-pro-25-watt-magsafe-charging</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T16:11:11-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T16:11:11-04:00</updated><title>这是我们对 iPhone 16 和 16 Plus 的初步了解</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;手持 iPhone 16 的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/e-O4RDUA93U1WeEki_6O0MU7inE=/4x0:3004x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574779/DSC08308.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;今年的颜色很好。&lt;/em>; |照片：Allison Johnson / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;cJozLP&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/e/24001058&quot;>;iPhone 16 和 16 Plus 是官方&lt;/a>;，操作按钮继承自&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23879619/apple-iphone-15-pro-max-review&quot;>;15 Pro&lt;/a>;和相机凸起的新外观。在宣布这一消息后，我们刚刚在加利福尼亚州库比蒂诺与他们进行了一些实际操作，好消息是颜色又回来了，宝贝：它们看起来很棒。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;wQtHOp&quot;>;后置摄像头现在垂直堆叠在较小的药丸状摄像头凸起上。这种安排更适合捕捉空间视频，以免我们忘记 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24054862/apple-vision-pro-review-vr-ar-headset-features-price&quot; >;Vision Pro&lt;/a>;。对于普通 iPhone 来说，它也只是一种新鲜的外观，苹果喜欢每隔几年推出一款来改变现状。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;照片：Allison Johnson / The Verge &lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;相机凸起向侧面移动。&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;TQ7L5K&quot;>;它们配备了与前代产品相同尺寸的屏幕：... &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24237940/iphone-16-hands-on-pictures-price-features-apple&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24237940/iphone-16-hands-on-pictures-price-features-apple" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24237940/iphone-16-hands-on-pictures-price-features-apple</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T15:34:55-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T15:34:55-04:00</updated><title> Apple Watch Series 10 上手：更大、更亮、更薄</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;手腕上的新款 Apple Watch Series 10&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HHsKf5umAvi_sFCpq0yTd3a6-hQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574669/series10close.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;戴在手腕上很轻。我很惊讶。&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;fclGhe&quot;>;现在 Apple 的 Glowtime 活动结束了，我们需要花一些时间来了解 &lt;a href=&quot;https:// /www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236801/apple-watch-series-10-price-specs-features-release-date&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 10&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =&quot;ig8mko&quot;>;今年是 Apple Watch 的 10 周年纪念日，但 Series 10 与您已知的并没有太大不同。它看起来很像之前的 Apple Watch 型号，但它采用了更新的设计，使整个包装变得更薄，同时将屏幕尺寸从 Series 9 的 41 毫米和 45 毫米扩大到 42 毫米和 46 毫米。自 Series 7 以来，42 毫米和 46 毫米的尺寸逐渐变大，佩戴时不会感到笨重。苹果&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2024/09/introducing-apple-watch-series-10/&quot;>;表示新显示屏的亮度提高了 40%&lt;/a>;，并且始终如一-on 模式现在每秒刷新一次，旧设备上每分钟刷新一次。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;漆黑...&lt;/em>;&lt; /figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24236958/apple-watch-series-10-hands-on-bigger-brighter-and-thinner&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip ;&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24236958/apple-watch-series-10-hands-on-bigger-brighter-and-thinner" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24236958/apple-watch-series-10-hands-on-bigger-brighter-and-thinner</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry></feed>